## Nest CLI commands
https://docs.nestjs.com/cli/usages

## Linting Command (Fixes everything automatically)
[https://stackoverflow.com/questions/40271230/how-to-run-eslint-fix-from-npm-script]
npm run lint -- --fix

## Libraries Installed
npm install dotenv --save

npm install --save @nestjs/config
[Nest provides a @nestjs/config package out-of-the-box to help load our .env file.]